| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4925 — Recovery Inhibition (ragnarlocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e1a5d335-9d18-5913-bc28-f7358a75b90d"
